                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="gotomarket/components/content/richtext"
                                text="&lt;h3>Worldline encourages employee mobility within the company so that each collaborator flourishes in his/her professional career.&lt;/h3>&#xa;&lt;p>Mobility is a personal development factor which is embedded in our culture and which contributes to enrich our professions.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>Professional and/or geographical mobility falls within the evolution prospects that we offer to our employees. It allows those who wish to, to benefit from coaching and mentoring ensured locally by recruiting managers.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>Each month, Worldline offers new career opportunities within Worldline but also at the Atos Group level.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;a class=&quot;button-blue alt&quot; href=&quot;https://jobs.atos.net/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>Find your job&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                        </column1>
